{"tid":1219630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我哋需要一支可以代表到我哋嘅旗","createTime":"2019-06-14T00:02:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T02:22:37.000Z","uid":18245,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"be744bf78fee68f20906360601f274e3129bfb92","tid":1219630,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:02:33.000Z","msg":"我地需要一支可以代表到我地嘅旗<br />\n唔係英國旗 因為英國唔鳩會埋我地<br />\n希望支旗可以帶到希望畀我地<br />\n令我地記得自己守護緊啲咩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5UoaLog.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5UoaLog.jpg&h=7880a01b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n象徵住香港人民對自由、和平同民主嘅熱愛同追求。<br />\n依家全世界望住我哋，我哋好應該利用今次機會比全世界知道呢佢嘅存在！&nbsp;<br />\n拿拿林整出嚟帶去示威和遊行！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地需要新區旗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1214306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1214306</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4b65e09a8bbecd516b810a53f3518c0272f65ad2","tid":1219630,"uid":61398,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:15:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ec2f4592599e89268c19957325ede5e82732966","tid":1219630,"uid":27458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:15:58.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"8db11eadd3cfc3eb2a729db7d1d600b45507c21f","tid":1219630,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:43:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82af44fc37ee7631c080c4796524f303e12fa21f","tid":1219630,"uid":66514,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:46:17.000Z","msg":"現成龍獅旗，建國後入返英聯邦"},{"pid":"bffcea1e4fc3fb04489c98701436051e65fd1c40","tid":1219630,"uid":127431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:46:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d340968b18ba36982f1733a18b695e03eb72ef29","tid":1219630,"ui