yle=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但最重要既係保護香港人!!!!!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時最少已經有11個香港人為咗我地被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當中包括為咗我地而食棍!!!中椒!!!同埋中槍既香港人!!!!!!<br />\n星期日上街我地一定要為佢地發聲!!!唔可以忘記佢地!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n大家集中目標:<br />\n1.撤回送中惡法<br />\n2.林鄭及相關官員必須問責下台<br />\n3.釋放所有被捕人士及保證不會檢控任何示威者<br />\n4.起訴涉嫌謀殺之警員及其上司<br />\n5.成立具效力之警方濫用暴力調查組織<br />\n6.釋放所有在囚政治人士,包括黃之鋒及梁天琦<br />\n<br />\n香港人,記得一個都不能小!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n唔可以放棄任何一個自己人!!!!!!</span></span>"},{"pid":"bdd946540db7acb6edd9cf353371c8aa6f7d21ed","tid":1219630,"uid":35592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:09:59.000Z","msg":"用獅子山個shape 做圖案"},{"pid":"7a54bfff0e4ef2aa0c43d736e269056027d1a18e","tid":1219630,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6555922b0cd447f69af7784026c8e77d5bffbeae","tid":1219630,"uid":227433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:59:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1219757/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1219757/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:21:22.000Z","msg":"呢個都好緊要"},{"pid":"1752e9be3081ce815ebd28792041697e2b8bb721","tid":1219630,"uid":13592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:22:37.000Z","msg":"咪拎返支fb謝左嘅花黎做"}]}